## Domain Documentation

Document in code or adjacent markdown:

- Order status state machine diagram
- Checkout flow sequence
- Promotion rule evaluation order
- Inventory reservation TTL behavior

Mermaid diagrams preferred for flows:

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    Client->>API: POST /checkout/sessions
    API->>Inventory: reserve()
    API->>Stripe: create PaymentIntent
    API-->>Client: client_secret
```

